U19 Motif enrichment analysis¶

Test enrichment for peaks linked to topic-specific genes¶

Procedure:

  1. added gene expression count matrix from scRNA-seq data to archR object
  2. performed co-accessibility to link peaks to genes
  3. test motif enrichment for peaks with high correlation with the expression levels of topic-specifi genes

Link peak to genes with co-accessibility analyses¶

A heatmap of peak-to-gene links from ArchR¶

The heatmap rows are clustered by k-means clustering based on k=25. The side-by-side heatmap of linked ATAC (left) and gene regions (right) shows the correspondence of peak-to-gene links between two dataset.
